{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2852690/extras/ezgif.com-overlay_3_.gif?t=1731063197\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2852690/extras/desc_1.png?t=1731063197\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Arcanum Fortuna</strong> is an asymmetrical strategy roguelike deckbuilder inspired by classic tarot cards with a unique karma mechanic. Set out to explore a world of mystery with your four-legged companion and meet a colorful cast of characters. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you find your purpose within? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2852690/extras/desc_line.png?t=1731063197\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2852690/extras/desc_2.png?t=1731063197\" />\u00a0 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Encounter <strong>22</strong> unique characters of the Major Arcana; on the battlefield as cards - and in conversation. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With <strong>28</strong> keywords every card is unique, allowing for versatile strategies </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Cards can evolve once their condition has been fulfilled, growing ever stronger </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Buy, trade and purge cards to tweak your deck to your liking </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> The <strong>16</strong> Minor Arcana cards support you - but don't underestimate their strength and necessity</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">What deck will you build?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2852690/extras/desc_characters.png?t=1731063197\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2852690/extras/desc_line.png?t=1731063197\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2852690/extras/desc_3.png?t=1731063197\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover synergies and find your playstyle - place your cards wisely. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2852690/extras/4af744dc7a1293dcceaa41ad742f20a5-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1731063197\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2852690/extras/desc_line.png?t=1731063197\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2852690/extras/desc_4.png?t=1731063197\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Karma is a distinctive resource that both you and the enemy must keep balanced at all times. Some cards may cost you karma, some may give it - but be careful, once you fall below zero, the debt is paid with your blood instead. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2852690/extras/d2b80789239fc3b35a357ad2eebde84b-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1731063197\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2852690/extras/desc_line.png?t=1731063197\" /><strong><i></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Venture forth - may the Wheel of Fortune spin ever in your favor.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2852690/extras/ezgif.com-animated-gif-maker_1_.gif?t=1731063197\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/sto